videos.headline: Disaster for Texas Tech on fourth down
videos.description: A bad snap for Texas Tech on fourth down gives Kansas State great field position in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Texas Tech stonewalls fourth-down run
videos.description: Kansas State's Alex Barnes dives on fourth-and-short in the red zone but Texas Tech comes up with the stop.

videos.headline: Kansas State blocks punt for a safety
videos.description: Brock Monty busts through the line to get a hand on the Red Raiders' punt and pick up a key 2 points for Kansas State.

videos.headline: Walker's sack forces fumble
videos.description: Kansas State takes the ball back after Reggie Walker knocks the ball out of the quarterback's hands as he was attempting a pass.

videos.headline: Second-string QB botches snap for Red Raiders
videos.description: Kansas State's Chase Johnston is there to pick up the fumbled snap by McLane Carter on his first action of the game.

videos.headline: Big guy TD called back by penalty
videos.description: Dalton Risner catches a touchdown much to the delight of Mike Golic Jr. but is ultimately called back because of a penalty.
